No. D-2496. In the Matter of Discipline of Daniel S. Orci, Jr. 562 U.S. 808, 131 S. Ct. 397,

178 L. Ed. 2d 262,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7533. October 4, 2010.

Daniel S. Orci, Jr., of St. Petersburg Beach, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable *263within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
